Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:06.82,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜ 忘れたいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:12.80,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ねえ 思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:24.47,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あたたかい頬に降る 涙の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:31.07,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜ ふるえながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:36.63,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今 求めあうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:43.26,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}君だけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:48.95,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}抱きしめたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:55.33,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蒼い星の海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:24:01.21,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波間に漂う羽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:07.27,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}消えてゆく哀しみは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:12.85,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}明日への祈りなの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:17.70,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Blueflow
