Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:06.82,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何想要忘却？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:12.80,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}请回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:24.47,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那温暖的脸颊上滑落而下的泪之请愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:31.07,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何你在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:36.63,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}现在寻求着何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:43.26,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}只有你无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:48.95,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}都想与你相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:55.33,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蔚蓝的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:24:01.21,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波浪间漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:07.27,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐渐逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:12.85,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向着明日的祈祷


